"2 cups cinnamon graham cracker crumbs (about 15 sheets)","1/2 cup finely chopped honey-roasted peanuts","1/2 cup butter, melted","1  (4-oz.) semisweet chocolate baking bar, chopped","2 cups whipping cream, divided","1  (8-oz.) package cream cheese, softened","1 cup creamy peanut butter","1/2 cup firmly packed light brown sugar","2 teaspoons vanilla extract","2  large bananas, sliced","  Toppings: sweetened whipped cream, chocolate syrup, chopped honey-roasted peanuts"